---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="disclaimer">
      <strong>Not medical advice.</strong> Ehvidence organizes and analyzes published
      data for educational purposes. No treatment is universally effective or risk-free.
      Consult a qualified clinician for personalized risk/benefit analysis before any
      treatment decision. Pooled estimates depend on correct study extraction; see the
      <a href={`${base}/methodology`}>methodology</a> for limitations.
    </div>
    <p>
      <a href={`${base}/`}>Topics</a> ·
      <a href={`${base}/methodology`}>Methodology</a> ·
      <a href={`${base}/glossary`}>Glossary</a> ·
      <a href={`${base}/faq`}>FAQ</a> ·
      <a href={`${base}/contribute`}>Add data</a>
    </p>
    <p class="small">© {year} Ehvidence · Data and analysis released under CC0 1.0 (public domain).</p>
  </div>
</footer>
